commitResults.messageTitle: Lesson commands: Add parsers and delete feature
commitResults.messageBody:
Currently, the system only supports adding and listing lessons. There is
no command to delete lessons or to parse user input for that feature.

This limits lesson management and prevents users from cleaning up their
subject lesson lists when lessons are no longer needed.

Changes made:
* add DeleteLessonCommand and DeleteLessonCommandParser
* improve AddLessonCommandParser and ListLessonsCommandParser for
  consistent validation
* define corresponding model methods (hasLesson, addLesson, deleteLesson)
  to support the new command

This change completes the lesson management flow (Add → List → Delete)
and improves the overall usability of the lesson feature.
